x = (x^1, x^2, x^3)
F
F(x) = F^1 \frac{\partial x}{\partial x^1} + F^2 \frac{\partial x}{\partial x^2} + F^3 \frac{\partial x}{\partial x^3}
\partial x/\partial x^i
\nabla
\nabla = (\nabla x^1) \frac{\partial}{\partial x^1} + (\nabla x^2) \frac{\partial}{\partial x^2} + (\nabla x^3) \frac{\partial}{\partial x^3}
\nabla x^i
\partial x/\partial x^i
\partial x/\partial x^2 = r \hat \phi
\partial(r \hat \phi)/\partial x^2
-x
(\nabla x^i) \parallel \partial x/\partial x^i
(\nabla x^i) \perp \partial x/\partial x^j
i \neq j
\partial x/\partial x^i = h_i \hat e_i
\nabla x^i = \frac{1}{h_i} \hat e_i
